    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Elite Pale Maw agents who serve as infiltrators and assassins. They wear nondescript clothing over light armour, with only a small entropy symbol hidden on their inner wrist. More disciplined and capable than standard soldiers. Deployed at Surt’s Forge to stop Kaelen during the ritual.</p>",
      "director": "<p><strong>ABILITIES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Zealot Blade</strong> (Main, Melee, Agility): T1 3 dmg; T2 6 dmg; T3 9 dmg.</li><li><strong>Heretic’s Mark</strong> (Main, Ranged 40ft, Presence): T1 2 dmg + marked; T2 4 dmg + marked; T3 6 dmg + marked.</li></ul><p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Coordinated Assault:</strong> +1 to attack rolls against enemies marked by another Pale Maw creature.</li><li><strong>Shadow Strike:</strong> If attacking from concealment, +1 to attack and +2 damage on a tier 2+ result.</li><li><strong>Infiltrator:</strong> Can blend into non-combat crowds; Intuition test opposed by Reason to spot as Pale Maw before they reveal themselves.</li></ul><p><strong>BEAT 18 TACTICS:</strong> Target Kaelen with Heretic’s Mark. Work with the Strike Leader to keep party busy while she finishes the ritual.</p>",
